<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>
      Invoice Transaksi
    </title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        color: #333;
      }
      
      .container {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
      }
      
      .header {
        background-color: #000;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      
      .content h1 {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      
      .content p {
        margin: 10px 0;
      }
      
      .content a {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        text-align: center;
      }
      
      .status {
        background-color: #000;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      
      .status.pending {
        color: #f0ad4e;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      
      .status.success {
        color: #5cb85c;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      
      .status.delivered {
        color: #0275d8;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      
      .details {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      
      .details table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      
      .details th,
      .details td {
        text-align: left;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      
      .details th {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      
      .product-image {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      
      .product-image img {
        max-width: 200px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      
      .footer {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f1f1f1;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
      }
      
      .footer a {
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      
      .btn-pov {
        background-color: #000;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: auto;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        display: block;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        POV
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h1>
          Hi, {{ name }},
        </h1>
        <p>
          Weâ€™re happy to inform you that your order with the number #{{ transaction.transactionNumber }} has been successfully processed.
        </p>
        <a class="btn-pov" href="{{ appDomain }}/transaction-result/{{ transaction.transactionNumber }}">View Order</a>
        <p>
          Your order is now being prepared and will be shipped shortly. We will notify you once your package is on the way.
        </p>
        <h4>
          Next Steps
        </h4>
        <ol>
          <li>
            Track your order status in the POV or click the following link: <a
              style="text-decoration: none;color: #000; font-weight: bold;"
              href="{{ appDomain }}/transaction-result/{{ transaction.transactionNumber }}"
            >Track Your Order</a>.
          </li>
          <li>
            If you encounter any issues, feel free to contact us through our Help Center.
          </li>
        </ol>
        <p>
          Thank you for shopping with Shopee! We hope you enjoy your purchase.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this email. Add <a href="mailto:contact@thepov-id.com">contact
          @thepov
          -id.com</a>to your email contact list to ensure emails from POV are delivered to your inbox.<br />
        Jl. Jend. Sudirman No.67, Karanganyar, Kec. Astanaanyar, Kota Bandung, Jawa Barat 40241
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
